### 2. 핵심 내용 검증

#### apps/mobile/package.json
- ✅ 모든 의존성 버전 스펙 일치 (expo `~52.0.0`, RN `0.76.x`, zustand `^4.5.0`, RNTP `^4.1.0` 등)
- ✅ `babel-plugin-module-resolver ^5.0.0` devDependencies에 명시 (impl 주의사항 반영)
- ✅ scripts: `start / ios / android / type-check / lint` 모두 존재

#### apps/mobile/tsconfig.json
- ✅ `extends: "expo/tsconfig.base"`, `strict: true`
- ✅ 8개 path alias 전체 일치 (`@screens`, `@components`, `@store`, `@services`, `@audio`, `@navigation`, `@hooks`, `@types`)

#### apps/mobile/babel.config.js
- ✅ `babel-preset-expo` + `module-resolver` plugin, alias 8개 일치

#### apps/mobile/App.tsx
- ✅ `SafeAreaProvider` + `StatusBar style="light"` 스펙 일치
- ✅ impl/03, impl/07 참조 주석 포함

#### apps/mobile/app.json
- ✅ `userInterfaceStyle: "dark"`, `backgroundColor: "#0D0F1A"` 일치
- ✅ iOS `UIBackgroundModes: ["audio"]` + 마이크·사진 권한 문구 일치
- ✅ Android permissions: `RECORD_AUDIO`, `FOREGROUND_SERVICE`, `FOREGROUND_SERVICE_MEDIA_PLAYBACK`
- ✅ plugins: `react-native-track-player` + `react-native-google-mobile-ads`

#### apps/api/pyproject.toml
- ✅ 전체 의존성 목록 확인 (fastapi, sqlalchemy, asyncpg, alembic, pydantic-settings, python-jose, passlib, celery, redis, boto3, httpx, structlog)
- ✅ build-backend: hatchling

#### apps/api/app/main.py
- ✅ `create_app()` factory 패턴, lifespan 컨텍스트
- ✅ CORS middleware (development=`"*"`)
- ✅ `docs_url` production 비활성화

#### apps/api/app/core/config.py
- ✅ pydantic-settings `BaseSettings`, env_file 로드
- ✅ `MOCK_GPU: bool = True` (개발환경 GPU mock 분기)
- ✅ `S3_ENDPOINT_URL: str | None = None` (R2 옵션)

#### apps/api/app/core/security.py
- ✅ RS256 JWT stub (impl 스펙: "JWT stub — impl/02에서 실제 구현")

#### apps/api/app/core/db.py
- ✅ async SQLAlchemy engine, `async_sessionmaker`, `DeclarativeBase`, `init_db()`

#### apps/api/alembic/env.py
- ✅ `async_engine_from_config` + asyncio.run — async-aware Alembic env

